$ System.Text.Encoding - GetEncoding()

The method `GetEncoding` of the → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Text/Encoding[`System.Text.Encoding`] class returns an encoding (`System.Text.Encoding`) for the
specified → Windows/development/code-page[code page].

→ Windows/PowerShell example:
code {
$iso_8859_1 = [System.Text.Encoding]::GetEncoding('iso-8859-1')
code }

sa:
  Such encodings are used, for example, in methods such as → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/IO/File/ReadAllText[`System.IO.File::ReadAllText()`] etc.
